Description: The masstools package contains a lot of base functions which can be used for 
    mass spectrometry and metabolomics data processing and analysis. For example,
    tandem mass spectrometry (MS2) matching, dot product calculation, etc. 
biocViews: Metabolomics, MassSpectrometry, Preprocessing, Visualization
